# TN-Check: Certified CSL Model Checking via Tensor-Train Decomposition

**TN-Check** implements Continuous Stochastic Logic (CSL) model-checking
algorithms natively on tensor-train (TT) / matrix product state (MPS)
compressed probability vectors of Chemical Master Equations (CMEs).  It never
materialises the full state space, enabling certified probabilistic
verification of stochastic reaction networks with 50–100+ molecular species —
far beyond the reach of explicit-state tools such as PRISM, Storm, or STAMINA.

---

## Architecture

```
 ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
 │                        CLI / Config                         │
 │                       (config.py)                           │
 └──────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┬────────────┘
            │                                     │
 ┌──────────▼──────────┐           ┌──────────────▼────────────┐
 │   CME Compiler      │           │   CSL Checker             │
 │  (cme/)             │           │  (checker/)               │
 │                     │           │                           │
 │  ReactionNetwork    │           │  CSL parser               │
 │  ──► MPO generator  │           │  Bounded/unbounded until  │
 │  Stoichiometry      │           │  Fixpoint iteration       │
 │  FSP bounds         │           │  Three-valued semantics   │
 │  Initial states     │           │  Satisfaction-set algebra │
 └──────────┬──────────┘           └─────────────┬─────────────┘
            │                                     │
 ┌──────────▼─────────────────────────────────────▼────────────┐
 │                    Time Integrators                         │
 │                   (integrator/)                             │
 │                                                             │
 │  TDVP (1-site / 2-site)  │  TT-Krylov  │  Uniformization  │
 │  Euler (adaptive)        │  DMRG steady-state              │
 └──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘
                            │
 ┌──────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────┐
 │              TT / MPS Arithmetic Engine                     │
 │                     (tensor/)                               │
 │                                                             │
 │  MPS & MPO data structures     Canonical forms (QR, SVD)   │
 │  SVD rounding & compression    Zip-up contraction          │
 │  Hadamard / Kronecker products Inner products & norms      │
 │  Transfer matrices & environments                          │
 └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

 ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐
 │ Error Cert.  │  │  Ordering    │  │  Adaptive    │
 │ (error/)     │  │ (ordering/)  │  │ (adaptive/)  │
 │              │  │              │  │              │
 │ Truncation   │  │ RCM          │  │ Greedy-      │
 │ tracking     │  │ Spectral     │  │ doubling     │
 │ FSP bounds   │  │ METIS        │  │ Bond-dim     │
 │ Non-neg.     │  │ partitioning │  │ monitoring   │
 └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘

 ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐
 │   Models     │  │  Verifier    │  │ Diagnostics  │
 │ (models/)    │  │ (verifier/)  │  │(diagnostics) │
 │              │  │              │  │              │
 │ Birth-death  │  │ Independent  │  │ Marginals    │
 │ Toggle switch│  │ certificate  │  │ Moments      │
 │ Repressilator│  │ verification │  │ KL divergence│
 │ Cascade      │  │ 9 soundness  │  │ Neg. mass    │
 │ Schlögl      │  │ checks       │  │ tracking     │
 └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘
```

---

## Module Map

| Module | Directory | Purpose |
|--------|-----------|---------|
| **Tensor Engine** | `tn_check/tensor/` | MPS/MPO data structures, SVD compression, canonical forms, contractions, Kronecker algebra |
| **CME Compiler** | `tn_check/cme/` | Reaction-network IR, propensity-to-MPO compilation, stoichiometry, FSP bounds, initial states |
| **Integrators** | `tn_check/integrator/` | TDVP (1-site & 2-site), TT-Krylov, uniformization (Fox–Glynn), Euler, DMRG steady-state |
| **CSL Checker** | `tn_check/checker/` | CSL parser, bounded/unbounded until, fixpoint iteration, three-valued semantics |
| **Error Certification** | `tn_check/error/` | Truncation-error tracking, FSP bounds, non-negativity monitoring, interval arithmetic |
| **Species Ordering** | `tn_check/ordering/` | RCM, spectral ordering, METIS graph partitioning for entanglement minimisation |
| **Adaptive Rank** | `tn_check/adaptive/` | Greedy-doubling rank controller with per-bond singular-value monitoring |
| **Model Library** | `tn_check/models/` | Biological model definitions (birth-death, toggle switch, repressilator, cascade, Schlögl) |
| **Verifier** | `tn_check/verifier/` | Independent certificate verification with 9 soundness checks, JSON trace serialization |
| **Diagnostics** | `tn_check/diagnostics.py` | Marginal extraction, statistical moments, KL divergence, negative-mass tracking |
| **Experiments** | `tn_check/experiments.py` | Automated experiment runner for benchmarking and validation |
| **Evaluation** | `tn_check/evaluation/` | Benchmark harness, PRISM/Storm/STAMINA comparison wrappers |
| **Configuration** | `tn_check/config.py` | Dataclass-based configuration for all subsystems |

